# 27. Validation

## Schema validation

Reject:

```text
Unknown fields
Duplicate IDs
Missing required fields
Unsupported schema versions
Invalid enum values
```

Use:

```rust
#[serde(deny_unknown_fields)]
```

on author-facing definitions.

## Reference validation

Check:

```text
Every surface references a valid texture
Every classifier references a valid surface
Every palette references valid surfaces
Every graph node references valid inputs
Every output node exists
```

## Graph validation

Check:

```text
No texture-node cycles
All required channels produced
No unreachable nodes
No division by zero
No invalid remap ranges
```

## GPU validation

Check:

```text
All array layers have matching dimensions
All layers have matching formats
All arrays have matching layer counts
Palette indices lie within array bounds
Uniform values are finite
```

## Classifier validation

Check:

```text
At least one fallback surface exists
Every biome can produce a valid surface
Every geology category has a valid base layer
Scores remain finite
Normalized weights sum approximately to one
No material region exceeds its palette budget
```

