# 29. Persistence

Do not save generated base texture pixels in each save game.

Save:

```text
Catalog ID
Catalog content hash
Generator version
World seed
Dynamic material overrides
Overlay deltas
Player-painted or constructed surface changes
```

The baseline surface classification can be regenerated from terrain fields and voxel material state.

For edited terrain:

```text
Regenerate density and base material
Apply saved voxel/material overrides
Reclassify exposed surfaces
Apply persistent overlay deltas
Remesh
```

This aligns with the existing deterministic terrain-delta approach. 

